<C>__{linda martin}
<D>__{i was...cadging at a bar in gardena. this mexican man raoul or jorge or something starting talking to me. i thought i was pregnant, and i was desperate wicked bad for money. he said he'd give me two hundred dollars to act in a nudie film.}
<A>__{she takes a large gulp of water.}
<C>__{linda martin }
